{"tid":2031674,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"下次有中國新聞可唔可以唔好講風涼話","createTime":"2020-05-23T14:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T14:43:59.000Z","uid":199592,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d7186272559aa16d4cb5a05537a2e6582be803d3","tid":2031674,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:19:12.000Z","msg":"從小粉紅到訪民　海歸女碩士受迫害家破人亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2031421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2031421</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔止呢一個post，通常一有中國新聞出嚟，下面一定有一大班人講風涼話，<span style=\"color: red;\">講抵死又有，玩膠話相信黨又有</span>。<br />\n<br />\n睇咗<span style=\"color: red;\">咁多年</span>呢啲新聞，第一次講可能好笑，第二次講就係戇鳩，講風涼話除咗自己爽之外其實係<span style=\"color: red;\">一啲意義都冇</span>。<br />\n<br />\n你笑佢一句相信黨，小粉紅就會因此唔相信黨㗎啦咩？全部comment都係咁，所以我哋先至仲停留喺<span style=\"color: red;\">圍爐</span>level<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解唔可以將呢一啲新聞進一步解釋，再話俾世界知中國無民主自由呢？</span>可能你覺得相同嘅例子已經夠多，但係比起講風涼話，將香港人閪嘅一面表露無遺，<span style=\"color: red;\">將一切可以用到嘅嘢當成自己嘅彈藥似乎更加明智</span>，香港嘅未來已經倒數緊，我哋可唔可以一齊生性少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 可能發緊晦氣<br />\n<br />\n民族自強 香港獨立"},{"pid":"0ed4312c202c95835ef632acdcb98c889649cc52","tid":2031674,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:20:24.000Z","msg":"要認真mode啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664b09cac129d1944ef753768d4d9d13965302a3","tid":2031674,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好慘好慘"},{"pid":"4e172f4f59946e2024b8bd4e261ba7950a4cf5cf","tid":2031674,"uid":348453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite